Transformers : The Last Knight is an upcoming American science fiction action film based on the toy line of the same name created by Hasbro .
It is the fifth installment of the live-action Transformers film series and a direct sequel to 2014 's Transformers : Age of Extinction .
The film was directed by Michael Bay , with Mark Wahlberg and Stanley Tucci reprising their roles from Age of Extinction alongside Josh Duhamel , Tyrese Gibson , and John Turturro from the first three movies .
Bay has stated this film marks his final picture in the franchise .
The film is set to be released on June 21 , 2017 by Paramount Pictures in 2D , 3D , and IMAX 3D .